alerts.content:
The Devonshire Street tunnel will be closed from 6pm Thursday 1 January until 5am Monday 19 January. 

Follow the detour signs for Chalmers Street or Railway Square.

You can still access and exit Central Station via Exit 1 Grand Concourse, Exit 2 Eddy Avenue, Exit 3 Elizabeth Street, Exit 5 Chalmers Street and Exit 6 Devonshire Street.

Listen for announcements, check information screens and transport apps for updates before getting on trains
